name: Persia Nexus 999
description:
Persia Nexus 999 MM Collage on Canvas, private collection
Animated with Light Tricks edited in Kinemaster.

This NFT features the music of Cut-Out “Theme from the Fun Machine Part 2” 
Cut-Out is a studio project by members of Pell Mell, Robert Beerman, Greg Freeman and Steve Fisk. This music is unreleased and is being used by permission.
